flowchart TD
    start[uninstallPluginOp] --> settings[从 settings.json 删除 enabledPlugins 条目]
    settings --> registry[removePluginInstallation\n按 scope+projectPath 过滤]
    registry --> check{isLastScope?}
    check -->|是| orphan[markPluginVersionOrphaned\n标记目录为 GC 候选]
    orphan --> opts[deletePluginOptions\n清除配置+密钥]
    opts --> data[deletePluginDataDir\n清除数据目录]
    data --> warn[检查反向依赖 → 仅警告]
    check -->|否| warn
    warn --> done[返回 success 结果]
